title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-16-2013 WED
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-16-2013 WED PODCAST







Wednesday, October 16, 2013
The Mayor, Mike, And Marijuana

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest: Denver Mayor, Michael Hancock answers listeners' questions
 during his monthly visit with Mike.



 - 10AM hour

Mike examines the AARP commercial which is actually an attack ad targeting Mike Coffman
 in the guise of information about social security.




 - 11AM hour

Mike discusses the Senate agreement on the debt ceiling.
